createAuction(address,uint256,uint256,ui.details: Creates a Auction cooresponding to _templateIdInitializes auction with the parameters passed

params._minimumPrice: Minimum price that the token should be valued for successful Auction
params._paymentCurrency: The currency the Auction accepts for payment. Can be ETH or token address
params._startPrice: Price you want to start auction. This should be maximum price you want token to be valued at
params._templateId: Id of the auction template to create
params._token: Address of token to be auctioned
params._tokenSupply: Total number of tokens to be auctioned
params._wallet: Address where collected funds will be forwarded to

params._goal: Minimum amount of funds to be raised in weis or tokens
params._paymentCurrency: The currency the crowdsale accepts for payment. Can be ETH or token address
params._rate: Number of token units a buyer gets per wei or token
params._templateId: Id of the crowdsale template to create
params._token: Address of the token for crowdsale
params._tokenSupply: The total number of tokens to sell in crowdsale
params._wallet: Address where collected funds will be forwarded to
